---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Get in touch with Section 75 Claim Helper."
>
  <article class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">

    <h1>Contact</h1>

    <p>
      Use the form below to get in touch. We aim to respond within two working days.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Before contacting us:</strong> We cannot advise on individual claims or tell you whether your specific case is likely to succeed. For guidance on your situation, use the <a href="/">eligibility checker</a>, read the <a href="/guide/">complete guide</a>, or consult a solicitor.
    </p>

    <p>We are happy to hear from you if you want to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Report a factual error or out-of-date information on the site.</li>
      <li>Flag a UK business failure we have not yet covered.</li>
      <li>Report a technical problem with the claim pack download.</li>
      <li>Make a press enquiry.</li>
    </ul>

  </article>

  <div class="mt-8 not-prose">
    <form
      action="https://formspree.io/f/mqenkgwn"
      method="POST"
      class="space-y-5"
    >
      <div>
        <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Name</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          id="name"
          name="name"
          required
          class="w-full rounded border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 focus:border-gray-500 focus:outline-none"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Email address</label>
        <input
          type="email"
          id="email"
          name="email"
          required
          class="w-full rounded border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 focus:border-gray-500 focus:outline-none"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Message</label>
        <textarea
          id="message"
          name="message"
          rows="5"
          required
          class="w-full rounded border border-gray-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 focus:border-gray-500 focus:outline-none"
        ></textarea>
      </div>
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="btn-primary"
      >
        Send message
      </button>
    </form>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-500">
      We do not share your contact details with third parties. See our <a href="/privacy/" class="underline">privacy policy</a> and <a href="/disclaimer/" class="underline">disclaimer</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
